import React from "react";
import { Navbar, Nav, NavDropdown } from "react-bootstrap";

function Menu() {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
      {/* Logo à esquerda */}
      <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Seu Logo Aqui</Navbar.Brand>
      
      <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
      <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
        <Nav className="mr-auto"></Nav>
        
        {/* Botões de perfil e sair à direita */}
        <Nav>
          {/* Botão de perfil */}
          <NavDropdown title="example@example.com" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="16"
                height="16"
                fill="currentColor"
                className="bi bi-person-circle"
                viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              >
                <path d="M11 6a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0" />
                <path
                  fillRule="evenodd"
                  d="M0 8a8 8 0 1 1 16 0A8 8 0 0 1 0 8m8-7a7 7 0 0 0-5.468 11.37C3.242 11.226 4.805 10 8 10s4.757 1.225 5.468 2.37A7 7 0 0 0 8 1"
                />
              </svg>{" "}
              Perfil
            </NavDropdown.Item>
            <NavDropdown.Divider />
            
            {/* Botão de sair */}
            <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="16"
                height="16"
                fill="currentColor"
                className="bi bi-box-arrow-right"
                viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              >
                <path
                  fillRule="evenodd"
                  d="M10 12.5a.5.5 0 1 1-.5.5h-8a.5.5 0 1 1-.5-.5v-9a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h8a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v2a.5.5 0 0 0 1 0v-2A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 9.5 2h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3.5v9A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 14h8a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5v-2a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0z"
                />
                <path
                  fillRule="evenodd"
                  d="M15.854 8.354a.5.5 0 0 0 0-.708l-3-3a.5.5 0 0 0-.708.708L14.293 7.5H5.5a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h8.793l-2.147 2.146a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.708z"
                />
              </svg>{" "}
              Sair
            </NavDropdown.Item>
          </NavDropdown>
        </Nav>
      </Navbar.Collapse>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default Menu;
